<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Hazardous Materials</title>
  <link href="http://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: #fff4f4;
      padding: 2rem;
      color: #222;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #e74c3c;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    th, td {
      padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      text-align: left;
    }
    th {
      background-color: #e74c3c;
      color: white;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    tr:nth-child(even) {
      background-color: #ffe6e6;
    }
    a.btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      background-color: #e74c3c;
      color: white;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    a.btn:hover {
      background-color: #c0392b;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('partials/back-button') %>


  <h1>Hazardous Materials</h1>
  <p>Manage and track inventory flagged as hazardous. Ensure proper handling and compliance with safety regulations.</p>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>SKU</th>
        <th>Item Name</th>
        <th>Type</th>
        <th>Hazard Type</th>
        <th>Qty On Hand</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>RM055</td>
        <td>Industrial Solvent</td>
        <td>Raw Material</td>
        <td>Flammable</td>
        <td>120 liters</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>FP078</td>
        <td>Battery Packs</td>
        <td>Finished Product</td>
        <td>Chemical</td>
        <td>35 pieces</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <a href="/home" class="btn">Back to Home</a>

</body>
</html>
